                <div class="row mt-30">
                    <div class="col-xl-1 col-lg-1 col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-1 mb-md-30 ">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xl-10 col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-sm-12 col-12 mb-md-30 ">
                        <div class="card-grid-4 text-center hover-up">
                            <h4 class="section-title mb-10 wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Message from Directors</h4>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-12 mb-md-30">
                                <div class="card-grid-4-info">
                                        <h5 class="mt-10 color-text-mutted">Chairman</h5>
                                   
                                    </div>
                                    <p align="justify">Shipping is an ever-changing field. New regulations and standards are developing every day as the global shipping industry evolves. This makes the jobs of ship management a very challenging and complicated sector. The challenges those are faced by the Managers are enormous. From my long experience at Sea and at Shore I believe Marine Hive can offer a win-win solution to all these predicaments. Marine Hive is run by professionals with expertise in international Ship Management, moreover we are always prepared to alter our procedures to accommodate the requirements of our clients, while contributing to the global effort to ensure safer shipping and cleaner oceans. You are cordially invited to join us. Our goal is to provide the maximum possible support to the owners.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-12 mb-md-30">
                                <div class="card-grid-4-info">
                                        <h5 class="mt-10 color-text-mutted">Managing Director</h5>
                                 
                                    </div>
                                    <p align="justify">I took Seafaring as a career in 1995 after completing my graduation from the Marine Academy Bangladesh. Twenty years passed by, through thick and thin, and I found myself as a Ship Manager, managing ocean going Oil and Chemical tankers for ASP Shipmanagement Singapore. I realized it’s time to settle down at home and give something back to the community. With this intention and after long hours of brain storming with my friends, together we incepted the idea of establishing an organization which can  offer professional service to all sides of the aisle, the owners, managers, seafarers, flag state and others stake holders of the maritime industry. I am grateful to Marine hive Family to provide me with such an opportunity. They have been instrumental in my endeavor to pursue excellence and achieve my goal of serving the maritime community of Bangladesh, and my promise remains to continue that to the best of my ability. Bon Voyage.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xl-1 col-lg-1 col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-12 mb-md-30 ">
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        
                        <h2 class="section-title mb-10 wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Meet Our Board of Directors</h2>
                      
                    </div>
                    @foreach (var item in Model)
                    {
                        <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12 mb-md-30">
                            <div class="card-grid-4 text-center hover-up">
                                <div class="image-top-feature">
                                    <figure>
                                        @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(item.Image))
                                        {
                                            <img alt="@item.DirectorName" src="@item.Image">
                                        }
                                        else
                                        {
                                            <img alt="@item.DirectorName" src="~/images/no-image.jpg">
                                        }

                                    </figure>

                                </div>
                                <div class="card-grid-4-info">
                                    <h5 class="mt-10">@item.DirectorName</h5>
                                    <p class="font-xs color-text-paragraph-2 mt-5 mb-5">@item.Designation</p>
                                    <div class="rate-reviews-small pt-5">
                                        <span class="card-briefcase">@item.CompanyPost</span>
                                        <div class="text-center mt-10">
                                            <a class="share-facebook social-share-link" href="@item.FacebookLink"></a>
                                            <a class="share-twitter social-share-link" href="@item.TwitterLink"></a>
                                            <a class="share-linkedin social-share-link" href="@item.LinkedInLink"></a>
                                        </div>


                                    </div>
                                    <p align="justify">@item.Details</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>


                    }


